Financial Strength You Can Count OnAssurant Specialty Property is the leader in bringing diverse insurance products and beneficial membership programs to consumers like you. We are part of Assurant, a Fortune 500 company with $30 billion in assets and $9 billion in annual revenue. Assurant Security CommitmentAt Assurant Specialty Property, ensuring your privacy is our primary objective. We will not sell your personal information or share it with non-Assurant companies to market their products to you. Through our state-of-the-art technology and heightened security infrastructure, we are committed to keeping your personal information safe. Privacy Policy.




