Assurant Product Protection








Assurant Product Protection
No matter how big or small your retail business, now you can drive revenue and build customer loyalty with a simple shopping cart solution. Assurant Product Protection is an on-demand software tool for e-tailers that allows your customers to quickly and easily add an extended protection plan to their purchase. 
Assurant Product Protection gives retailers an immediate boost in revenue and attach rates. And customers get increased peace of mind and as well as improved satisfaction with their purchase.
Broad coverage. Deep experience.
Assurant Product Protection can provide coverage for over 25 product categories, from small appliances to home and garden to watches and jewelry. No matter what you sell, chances are we can cover it.
No need to worry about customer service.
Assurant provides 24/7 claims and support right from the start. Your customers get dedicated support from protection plan experts and you get all the credit!
How it works.
Assurant Product Protection is a flexible program that fits the way you do business. Opt for a simple plug-in, or ask about our API driven solution for a more tailored approach. 
Easy set up.
Assurant Product Protection is simple to set up, with onboarding typically taking less than 1 week for your retail site. And it’s fully compatible with leading e-commerce platforms.  Also, Assurant’s flexible platform supports point of sale and missed point of sale initiatives as well. 


Let’s work together


